query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 10 AND q.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('animation',
'asp.net-mvc-4',
'compiler-construction',
'concurrency',
'fonts',
'garbage-collection',
'ggplot2',
'ios8',
'orm',
'parsing',
'pdf',
'servlets',
'tomcat',
'variables',
'visual-c++');
